description:
*Available in: English*

*Note: This app is intended for use ONLY by new or professional lawyers*

New in 1.1.0:
- New UI and design
- 3 new Objection! sounds
- 4 new Hold it! sounds
- 4 new Take that! sounds
- 3 new Other sounds
- 5 new pictures

New in 1.0.2:
- Clearer Edgeworth picture in gallery
- 2 new pictures

New in 1.0.1:
- Less "schwing" from Phoenix Wright Objection!
- 8 new sounds
- 2 new pictures

This is the BEST Phoenix Wright app you can find on iPhone, Android, or webOS!

OBJECTION!

Have you ever gotten yourself into a situation where you were defending someone who was accused of murder and you saw a contradiction in the witness's testimony, but couldn't yell objection!? Well now you can!

This application contains objection, hold it, take that, and other sounds from Phoenix Wright, Miles Edgeworth, & many more characters of the amazingly epic Phoenix Wright video game series! It also comes with an awesome picture gallery!

Check out our other apps:
- Aquarium
- Fireplace
- Beach
- American Flag
- Rick Roll
- Solar System
- It's a Trap!
- Metal Gear Solid Soundboard
